    "description": "Care Hospitals has an exciting opening for a Surgeon at our Tiruchirappalli office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Care Hospitals:\nCare Hospitals is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Care Hospitals!",
